<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>联系客服</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/app.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="public-page">
  <main class="lead-panel mx-auto">
    <h1 class="h4 mb-2"><%= campaign.campaign_name %></h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-3">请提交手机号或线索编号，用于为你分配客服。</p>
    <% if (error) { %><div class="alert alert-danger"><%= error %></div><% } %>
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      您的手机号仅用于客服分配和避免重复分配，不会用于未经同意的营销群发。
    </div>
    <form method="post" action="/go/<%= campaign.slug %>?country=<%= countryCode %>">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label" for="lead_identifier">手机号或线索编号</label>
        <input class="form-control" id="lead_identifier" name="lead_identifier" value="<%= leadIdentifier %>" autocomplete="off" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-check mb-3">
        <input class="form-check-input" id="consent" name="consent" type="checkbox" required>
        <label class="form-check-label" for="consent">我同意提交信息用于客服分配</label>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary w-100" type="submit">继续联系客服</button>
    </form>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
